      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels weird that you say that. like you're actually agreeing with me. most people would tell me i'm being dramatic or that i have friends or something, but you're just... saying it's okay to just let go. it's kind of peaceful hearing that, but also scary. do you really think it would just be that easy? to just stop?",
